title: SneakerCon
text:
1. Place rare sneakers in Special Box for car loading. Rest of sneakers can be placed in iKEA duffle bags.
2. Have inventory list ready with sizes in numerical order with 3 prices. 
3. Share business sticker with everyone, buyer or not.

title: Sneaker Release Date
text:
